description: OnoPops provides delicious, refreshing, gourmet treats that are handmade in Hawaii using local and organic resources.Only the freshest quality ingredients are used to create innovative and creative flavor combinations that pay homage to both the Mexican paleta and Hawaiian regional cuisine traditions. Multiple generations of talented local cooks and bakers have developed certain tastes and textures for an obvious reason: that they are Ono.  We honor this tradition.
name: Ono Pops
